Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,2000)\pos(640,460)\bord0}阿兰达斯联合王国  国境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,630)\c&HFAFAFA&\be1}因戈尔米亚军    东北方面前线部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友军已经开始攻击了 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,争夺大陆霸权的两方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯联合王国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及因戈尔米亚多国统合体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对拥有丰富资源的阿兰达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈尔米亚在南下过程中集结多国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断增强国力军力 步步紧逼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰达斯方的战线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于节节败退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已收缩至国境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fsp0\bord1.5}Great Wall{\fscx600}\h\N{\r}此处 长城如铜墙铁壁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈尔米亚的攻击多次受挫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗眼看要进入胶着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军正不断集结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大阿兰达斯建国以来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长城曾无数次抵挡下蛮族入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可慌的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所言正是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我国拥有无数光辉历史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶上我们来视察 不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉下面 会带他们打赢这场苦战的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 都这会儿了还{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的心情我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让将军们也立刻动身前往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:01:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让他们碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的只是振奋军心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侵略?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军争?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是解放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌国虽丰饶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人民生活幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案是否
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位高权重者只知中饱私囊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剥削
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为满足私欲挑起战争所致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧 诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救阿兰达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将邻国的国民与国土 从腐败政权手中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗是解放战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敢于如此下定论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这胆量值得学习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fsp0\bord1.5}Bloody Hopper{\fscx1350}\h\N{\r}跃动死神队已成功侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部队向正门移动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩护不要疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳伦斯 别提前打开酱汁包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这类军粮 要把米铺在盘子上蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁这时间打开酱汁包正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啥区别嘛 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 所以你才是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是 知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦 快点弄好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也好不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候更该拿出骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳伦斯先生 光琉 快点给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急什么 老夫来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字队长 该吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铃城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚放下行李 但要对不住他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被记恨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 独立第八部队放弃这一要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻转移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃大型车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迅速整理食物及武器弹药等可携带资源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 还吃什么吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃两口饭怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜 有空就把这个搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新来的 准备好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分明刚刚才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对什么有不满
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,食物? 命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 这不挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说算是吃到饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有条不紊有条不紊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想幸福你也得琢磨一下品味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,品味{\rsymbol}…{\r}吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 战场上品味很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了 回头聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲机 劳伦斯机 时宗机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备完毕立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱了队形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你连控制机体走路都不会?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解 时宗机会好好走路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么口气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的机师们真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且慢 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在后方指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方部队正等着将军的激励
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经刻不容缓 请立刻{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战场上随机应变最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们如今的使命只不过是视察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的吧 泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须返回西北方面军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快制定出反攻计划才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 听好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传令下去 就算全军覆没 也要死守这座基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通电全军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老头子们在现场捣了不少乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵力本就悬殊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本打不赢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到我方暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活着回到<不退之门> 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是他的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您指泉大佐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们莫非一直在逃跑?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么回事 连这个都不知道就跟着走?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那友军们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是待在那个偏僻地带 本来能去营救的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜我们为什么被安排在那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被嫌弃了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你挺聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是正义的伙伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算我们去了 又能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杯水车薪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别婆婆妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们听队长的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟着他 我们就不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说 这些事等你独当一面后在考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能独当一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord0\bord1.5\fsp0}TRAIL KRIEGER{\fscx1450}\h\N{\r}两台曳战者先导 席加负责支援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上阵了呢 新来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怕 在生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得先撸一发放松放松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意周围
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不愧是班长 知道得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面山谷里没有水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是条能走的道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前搬运物资时曾走过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近就不知怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们出生前 那边也是河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长 行进路线上发现被毁车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是受到了人为袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经进因戈尔米亚的势力范围了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,召回曳战者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路线保持不变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本队暂时待机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲机 时宗机继续前进 探明周围状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迂回进山里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别摔跤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 在学校学过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不能松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方有人开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车辆行驶声 正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有友方部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近未确认到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动哦 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平民?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭受攻击的 是平民卡车及所属不明的装甲车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追击方是因戈尔米亚军的拖车 以及两台曳战者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在需尽早与大部队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能进行无谓的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个推理也成立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道要让平民等死?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武装的平民?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风险太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<如果>不过是个假设 不能让战友冒风险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令 进时宗上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皆骏先生 皆骏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续确认周围状况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出最适路线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然不想牺牲战友 那我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了 这曳战者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是多少来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点 快一点 吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是平民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑住 时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再坚持10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑{\rsymbol}…{\r}撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂 我懂是懂{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴 怎么能逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这闹不好是要掉脑袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当兵的肯定不懂啦 大软蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来救你的 就不能客气点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord1.5\fsp0}Argevollen Stabilis Prima\N{\r}银色歼灭者稳定型原型机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色{\rsymbol}…{\r}啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总比被抢走强 总比被毁掉强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要驾驶它 驾驶它逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能驾驶就早驾驶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不会{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只能拼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 装置 唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统启动流程 运行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辨识密码 0612 0530
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新录入 吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是机师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 多好的点子 我真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我驾驶吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁 增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动 然后战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是问那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动程序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该先确认哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动程序{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握住操纵杆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想着要做什么 在脑中想象出实景进行操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意别胡乱尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想象?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙动起来没有延迟 完全按照我思维在动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么没打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,节奏太强了啊 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你太废了吧 还什么节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字队长 那是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:06.45,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}この高き無望の空でいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:11.07,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}その意思は膝を立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:19.83,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:22.34,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.15,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:31.90,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.39,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.27,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.08,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:52.22,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:57.47,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:02.04,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:03.29,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(10,660)\an1}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:07.67,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:14.30,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.85,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:23.61,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.35,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.27,0:22:06.45,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 向着这无望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.45,0:22:11.07,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志将一飞冲天
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.15,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是战友吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.41,0:22:31.90,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}当走之路是黑暗吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.39,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光闪动
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.27,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无名感情在胸中翻涌
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.08,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此时此刻在此地 尚不能结束-
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.08,0:22:52.22,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那么就做好活下去的准备吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.34,0:22:57.47,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔热忱 越积越高无处释放
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.47,0:23:02.04,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.42,0:23:07.67,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}战场之上 笑谈青涩有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.67,0:23:14.30,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我会一个一个亲自去实践
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.85,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放马过来{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
